1 zw/w foto met stempel Den Kongelige Kobberstiksamling Kobenhavn; notitie in onbekend handschrift: Pen 130 x 92 mm; Notitie FG: Copenhagen, cf. Towers & Gates of Amsterdam 1562 (Tolnay 41-43) which are however much larger cf also Bastelaer 40; Bottom left: (?) P. Bruegel (?) Hondius probably after Bruegel (?). Hondius may be correct; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. A drawing of similar style by Hondius in Coll. Baron Paul Hatvany.'
